               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I went to bathe; the prosecutor was standing by the side of the canal - I took up my hat, and the bundle which was lying beside it; I looked at it, and a person called to me to take it to him - I was going to him, and he ran away; I went back to the prosecutor and was taken.</p>
